channel.title: Debian 10 virtualbox not working
channel.description:
On fresh Debian 10 buster here is my error:
''Failed to open a session for the virtual machine Whonix-Gateway-XFCE
Result Code: NS_ERROR_FAILURE (0x80004005) Component: MachineWrap Interface: IMachine {85632c68-b5bb-4316-a900-5eb28d3413df} ''
''Failed to open a session for the virtual machine Whonix-Workstation-XFCE.
The virtual machine 'Whonix-Workstation-XFCE' has terminated unexpectedly during startup with exit code 1 (0x1).
Result Code: NS_ERROR_FAILURE (0x80004005) Component: MachineWrap Interface: IMachine {85632c68-b5bb-4316-a900-5eb28d3413df} ''
How can I solve? no change was made imported vanilla. on Windows 10 whonix was working ok... Im suing a lenovo M92p thinkcenter.
